thread.title: Jack Wills
thread.title_full: Chinese Motorcycle Parts Online reviewed by Jack Wills

author: Jack Wills
title: Jack Wills
text:
New disk brake calliper arrived in 2 days to central London, it was well-packaged and in great condition. Would order from CMPO again they had everything I needed for my bike and it was fairly priced too.
One downside is that the calliper did not come with fitting instructions.
I have a 2013 Lexmoto Arizona 125cc and they have a huge selection of parts for my bike.
